instance virtual_to_physical_interaction : DTDFVocab:VirtualToPhysical [
    base:desc "Control commands are sent from the Digital Twin to the incubator by publishing messages to RabbitMQ queues dedicated to the fan and the heatbed. The controller software on the Raspberry Pi listens to these queues, decodes the received commands and actuates the fan and heatbed (e.g., setting fan speed or heat‑bed power). The controller provides implicit feedback by continuing to publish sensor data that reflects the effect of the command."
